data.description: Check out this completely updated ranch in Sherwood Forest. Fresh paint, newer windows, updated flooring plus kitchen and bath remodel in 2023. Spacious living room plus dining area. Kitchen with breakfast bar and access to deck. Basement features a wood shop area, bonus room for extra living space, plus partially finished family room ready for your finishing touches. Attached garage. Home warranty provided with accepted offer.
